    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone needing a functional daily driver. The exterior shows its age with several visible scratches, minor dings, and some paint fading on the hood and roof. Inside, the cabin is clean but displays noticeable wear on the upholstery and some minor staining on the carpets. Mechanically, the car runs well, though it may soon require routine maintenance like new brake pads or tires. It is a solid, honest vehicle for someone prioritizing reliability over a perfect appearance.",
