      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector-grade specimen that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, protected by a premium ceramic coating that makes the paint pop. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the hand-stitched leather retains its original texture and scent, with absolutely no signs of wear on the bolsters or touchpoints. Every electronic feature, from the adaptive driver assistance suite to the premium surround-sound audio system, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been strictly garage-kept and serviced exclusively at authorized intervals. With exceptionally low mileage and a documented history of preventative care, this is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in flawless, showroom condition.",
